de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface ResourceProviderA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConnectionType, DeviceType, DuctType, LocationType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConnectionTypeImpl, DeviceTypeImpl, DuctTypeImpl, LocationTypeImpl, ResourceProviderAImpl

    public interface ResourceProviderA
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Resource Provider A'. An abstract base class for resource providing elements, e.g. devices, locations, ...

    The following features are supported:

    • Provided Bundles
    • Possible Resource Provisions
    • Provided Groups
    • Resource Links
    See Also:
    LibraryPackage.getResourceProviderA()

        Returns the value of the 'Possible Resource Provisions' reference list. The list contents are of type ResourceType. A possibility to declare possible resource types for this resource provider before the actual resource instances are declared

      • getProvidedGroups

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<ResourceGroup> getProvidedGroups()
        Returns the value of the 'Provided Groups' containment reference list. The list contents are of type ResourceGroup. Resource groups can organize the resource of a provider, e.g. to represent connectors.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Provided Groups' containment reference list.
        See Also:
        LibraryPackage.getResourceProviderA_ProvidedGroups()

      • getResourceLinks

        org.eclipse.emf.common.util.EList<ResourceLink> getResourceLinks()
        Returns the value of the 'Resource Links' containment reference list. The list contents are of type ResourceLink. Resource dependencies specify the interconnection of resources in the resource provider, e.g. to represent power distribution and galvanic isolation.
        Returns:
        the value of the 'Resource Links' containment reference list.
        See Also:
        LibraryPackage.getResourceProviderA_ResourceLinks()
